<A>__{ziat leaning in close, over the stove in the kitchen, framed by guards. it is the same crouched posture he always uses to work the stove but now his eyes show complete despair as he sees: a thousand shreds of paper money floating in his pots amid his withered tea bags. from ashes to ashes and dust to dust. ziat folds his head into his hands, sobbing then wailing very human, very sad.}
